nodes.name: long-chain-fatty-acid:[acyl-carrier-protein] ligase (AMP-forming)
nodes.rxn: ATP + Long-chain fatty acid + Acyl-carrier protein <=> AMP + Diphosphate + Long-chain acyl-[acyl-carrier protein]

nodes.name: Alkane,reduced-rubredoxin:oxygen 1-oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: Alkane + 2 Reduced rubredoxin + Oxygen + 2 H+ <=> 2 Oxidized rubredoxin + Primary alcohol + H2O

nodes.name: rubredoxin:NAD+ oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: 2 Reduced rubredoxin + NAD+ + H+ <=> 2 Oxidized rubredoxin + NADH

nodes.name: primary_alcohol:NAD+ oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: Primary alcohol + NAD+ <=> Aldehyde + NADH + H+

nodes.name: fatty acid,[reduced NADPH---hemoprotein reductase]:oxygen oxidoreductase (omega-hydroxylating)
nodes.rxn: Fatty acid + Oxygen + [Reduced NADPH---hemoprotein reductase] <=> omega-Hydroxy fatty acid + [Oxidized NADPH---hemoprotein reductase] + H2O

nodes.name: fatty acid,reduced-flaboprotein:oxygen oxidoreductase (RH-hydroxylating or -epoxidizing)
nodes.rxn: [Reduced NADPH---hemoprotein reductase] + Fatty acid + Oxygen <=> alpha-Hydroxy fatty acid + [Oxidized NADPH---hemoprotein reductase] + H2O

nodes.name: Palmitate:CoA ligase (AMP-forming)
nodes.rxn: ATP + Hexadecanoic acid + CoA <=> AMP + Palmitoyl-CoA + Diphosphate

nodes.name: rubredoxin:NAD+ oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: 2 Reduced rubredoxin + NAD+ + H+ <=> 2 Oxidized rubredoxin + NADH

nodes.name: aldehyde:NAD+ oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: Aldehyde + NAD+ + H2O <=> Fatty acid + NADH + H+

nodes.name: Fatty acid,reduced rubredoxin:oxygen oxidoreductase (omega-hydroxylating)
nodes.rxn: Fatty acid + Oxygen + 2 Reduced rubredoxin + 2 H+ <=> omega-Hydroxy fatty acid + 2 Oxidized rubredoxin + H2O
